  "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
  "body": "In a team collaboration setting, if the team is not in sync and different members have a different metadata_region in their .heirloom.yml file, then data related to heirloom can be fragmented and out of sync.  Although not trivial, it might make sense to have a locking mechanism that allows there to be only one master metadata region at a time.\n"
